            "jpName": "伝説の語り部",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そしてボクは気づく！　敗因は……王の慈悲。\n他の出走者に心を向けすぎたのだ。\n――悔い改め、次こそ世代最強の座へ。",
            "enText": "And then I realize! The reason for my \ndefeat was the mercy of the…… king. I \nwas too focused on the other runners. \n―I will repent, and next time I will \nbe the strongest of my generation.",
